Colour of fresh specimens . Head and body silvery, sometimes with a black spot at center of each scale showing dotted lines. Interorbital, snout and infraorbital area yellow to orange with blackish. Dorsal, caudal and pectoralfins yellow to orange shade; dorsal-fin with a wide black margin; caudal fin with a very fine black edge which disappears with age growth over 30 cm SL (
Iwatsuki & Heemstra, 2011
); pelvic and anal-fin rays dense black.
